            <title><![CDATA[中国东部战区多军种力量在东海海空域实施联合警巡]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-08/18.jpg?Vni6O_H_TN5IHQQiyOpmFpIBtOIxGIh7&itok=zRjrfMOQ" alt data-caption="中国东部战区出动作战舰艇、歼轰机等多军种力量，在东海当面海空域实施联合警巡。图为飞机带弹出动。（“东部战区”微信公号）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-08/18.jpg?Vni6O_H_TN5IHQQiyOpmFpIBtOIxGIh7&itok=zRjrfMOQ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
